methods.name: public CollectionInfo.Builder setRowCount(int rowCount)
methods.comment:
* Sets the row count.
             * @param rowCount The number of rows in the collection.
             * @return This builder.

methods.name: public CollectionInfo.Builder setColumnCount(int columnCount)
methods.comment:
* Sets the column count.
             * @param columnCount The number of columns in the collection.
             * @return This builder.

methods.name: public CollectionInfo.Builder setHierarchical(boolean hierarchical)
methods.comment:
* Sets whether the collection is hierarchical.
             * @param hierarchical Whether the collection is hierarchical.
             * @return This builder.

methods.name: public CollectionInfo.Builder setSelectionMode(int selectionMode)
methods.comment:
* Sets the selection mode.
             * @param selectionMode The selection mode.
             * @return This builder.

methods.name: public CollectionInfo.Builder setItemCount(int itemCount)
methods.comment:
* Sets the number of items in the collection. Can be optionally set for ViewGroups with
             * clear row and column semantics; should be set for all other clients.
             *
             * @param itemCount The number of items in the collection. This should be set to
             *                  {@code UNDEFINED} if the item count is not known.
             * @return This builder.

methods.name: public CollectionInfo.Builder setImportantForAccessibilityItemCount(int importantForAccessibilityItemCount)
methods.comment:
* Sets the number of views considered important for accessibility.
             * @param importantForAccessibilityItemCount The number of items important for
             *                                            accessibility.
             * @return This builder.
